{
  "stem": "21812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We sold our apartment, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because we knew that we were-- we would have to leave.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we sold our apartment and moved in with my grandmother, who had extra rooms.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I sort of apprenticed myself out to that tailor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I learned to do all kinds of things, and was very helpful.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can still sew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that was one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then I went to the-- it lasted a little bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I went to the Jewish organization that I mentioned before, the Zionist organization, which were-- which was preparing kids to-- for going to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I went there, and that was sort of a club-- club affair, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was more than just the-- it prepared us in many ways.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remembered we got lec-- we had lectures about health.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my first sex lecture was given there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they introduced us to a lot of different areas, prepared us to, you know, to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Zionist group.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember which-- which arm it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have no idea whether it was Jabotinsky or another one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember that anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was one possibility, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Except that, you know, we knew it was all illegal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were the illegal transport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no legal way of getting into Palestine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was based on the hope that somehow you would get on one of those illegal ships.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were doing both.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whoever could emigrate would emigrated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My-- the first one to leave was an uncle, Uncle Willy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I, as a matter of fact, liked him very much because he was a very outgoing guy, very free spirit.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
